god_leader_d: §7A leader of supreme power and wisdom, guiding his followers towards victory and glory.
Wind_Ranger_d: §7In ancient legends, there exists a mysterious entity called the 'Messenger of the Wind'. He is an elegant and powerful elf with the ability to control wind elements.
FenrirArrow_d: Launch a piercing wind arrow that deals 100% damage to the first target and 70% damage to a second target behind. Creates a small area of knockback and slows enemies for 1-2 seconds. (8-12s cooldown)
skill.mist_arrow.description: Shoots a special arrow made of glowing spores. Upon impact, it explodes into a thick smoke cloud (radius 4-5 blocks) lasting 5-7 seconds. Enemies inside take minor poison damage and significant slowdown.
